2,"uid":52024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Major係乞食科<br />\n唯有minor CS叫有一技旁身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame, 不過本身對programming都有d興趣, 用黎幫自己計數"},{"pid":"2375ce4a68ca60178d912b332d59c4c618c055d8","tid":87012,"uid":52024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>吓?! 宜家仲教OOP? 已經冇以前咁流行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁依家教咩?<br />\nfunctional programming?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心，OOP初學好好玩<br />\n但係真係煩到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得學pattern最麻煩, 好難記<br />\n但係實際做野就發覺好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然都唔到我寫)"},{"pid":"0a86616b7e270537137a8cf5f275a018fccd6c4f","tid":87012,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>吓?! 宜家仲教OOP? 已經冇以前咁流行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁依家教咩?<br />\nfunctional programming?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心，OOP初學好好玩<br />\n但係真係煩到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得學pattern最麻煩, 好難記<br />\n但係實際做野就發覺好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然都唔到我寫)</blockquote><br />\nPattern我冇乜點記 總之明個精神就好容易知道會用D咩方法<br />\n但係一接手既時候，你唔知OBJECT既STATE會唔會突然轉左，好頭痕"},{"pid":"796ac07aaa1b845cdd754c46349b01a707e681dc","tid":87012,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"細電狗算唔算仲慘過it 狗<br />\n利申Programming 唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學緊少少matlab"},{"pid":"b983c010f3380eedccf985edb5581fc5513a6778","tid":87012,"uid":68115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"本身完全無讀過it<br />\n但係由細到大屋企學校朋友電腦什至psp改機都係我攪<br />\n無啦啦入左間公司做上公司維修電腦printer 先開始讀it<br />\n跟住又好好彩入到間公司做internal support<br />\n之後先讀返個high dip(重未讀完)<br />\n中間又好好彩又俾我轉到大公司做 可以試既野重多<br />\n<br />\n其實想講既係我係因為工作而選擇讀it<br />\n我算係好彩既一個<br />\n<br />\n利申2x 連high dip都未有 20k/m"},{"pid":"a6ccacc683f503b710658b61318e754d63217d75","tid":87012,"uid":63518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"細個覺得hacker好型 中學就揀左ict<br />\n讀落發覺algorithm呢樣野好有趣<br />\n一路學係一路改良緊自己嘅思維<br />\n自己programming成績又唔錯 有成功感<br />\n於是對相關嘅野愈黎愈有興趣<br />\n加上聽講CS出路唔錯<br />\n大學就major左CS<br />\n呢樣野變左自己真正嘅興趣 <br />\n注定呢世做IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc4b5f072b20827a777b4d8d74cfca0ce11c52c","tid":87012,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"揀錯科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cc8eea056cf12070ebd9d265f6f66ba1d2cd98","tid":87012,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"因為 0 同 1 既世界有無限可能"}]}